README

Unicorn HAT HD provides a matrix of 256 RGB LED pixels. It's ideal for writing messages, showing graphs, and drawing pictures.

Learn more: https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/unicorn-hat-hd
For examples run: `curl -sS get.pimoroni.com/unicornhathd | bash`

IMPORTANT

Unicorn HAT HD requires spi.
To enable run `curl get.pimoroni.com/spi | bash`
or use raspi-config and reboot your Raspberry Pi.
